    "To facilitate the evaluation of the artifact, we downsized our experiments, employing fewer fuzzers, subjects, and iterations.",
    "[How to] Run two fuzzers, CHATAFL and AFLNET, on the three subjects kamailio, pure-ftpd, and live555, respectively, iterating the process 5 times.",
    "Each execution takes place within a container and spans a duration of 360 minutes.",
    "Consequently, this experiment involves a total of 30 containers, with each container running fuzzing for 240 minutes and coverage collection for 120 minutes.",
